{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:10NordicMesh15GenericDeltaSetV19continueTransactionSbvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"title":"continueTransaction","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericDeltaSet\/continueTransaction"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericDeltaSet"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"carrying cumulative values of the field."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"more seconds earlier."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericdeltaset\/continuetransaction"]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/GenericDeltaSet/continueTransaction":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericDeltaSet\/continueTransaction","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericdeltaset\/continuetransaction","title":"continueTransaction","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/GenericDeltaSet":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GenericDeltaSet","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericDeltaSet","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericdeltaset","title":"GenericDeltaSet","type":"topic","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"GenericDeltaSet","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"}}}